Racial Immunity						KEY:Killoren ~ Racial Immunity		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.Killoren Race Trait.SpecialQuality				DESC:Immunity to magic sleep effects and a +2 racial bonus on saves against enchantment spells or effects.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.
