Resist Enchantment					KEY:Elven Hound ~ Resist Enchantment	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.Race Trait.Elven Hound Race Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:Like their elf masters, elven hounds have a +2 racial bonus on saving throws against enchantment spells or effects.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.190
Sprint							KEY:Elven Hound ~ Sprint			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.Race Trait.Elven Hound Race Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:Although an elven hound can go head to head with many creatures, its strength lies in the chase. Once per hour, an elven hound can move five times its normal speed (250 feet) when it makes a charge.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.190
